      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Bake the sponge layers, 30 to 35 minutes",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Heat the oven to 170°C fan. Grease and line two 20 cm round cake tins. Whisk the {{vegetable-oil}}, {{eggs}}, and {{vanilla-extract}} together in a large bowl. Stir in the {{light-brown-sugar}}. Fold in the {{plain-flour}}, {{baking-powder}}, {{bicarbonate-of-soda}}, {{cinnamon-ground}}, {{ginger-ground}}, and {{fine-sea-salt}}. Add the grated {{carrot}} and {{walnuts}} and fold until evenly distributed. Divide between the tins and bake for 30 to 35 minutes until a skewer comes out clean. Cool in the tins for 10 minutes, then turn out onto a rack to cool completely.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the frosting and assemble",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Beat the {{unsalted-butter}} until smooth. Beat in the cold {{cream-cheese}} until just combined. Add the {{icing-sugar}} and {{vanilla-extract}} and beat briefly until smooth. Do not overbeat or the frosting will become too loose. Place one sponge layer on a plate or board. Spread one-third of the frosting over the top. Place the second layer on top and spread the remaining frosting over the top and sides. Press walnut halves from the remaining {{walnuts}} around the top edge. Refrigerate for at least 1 hour before serving.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
